name: goBTC
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Bitcoin >< Algorand. goBTC are fully collateralised with native BTC, giving BTC the full power of the Algorand blockchain including its carbon neutrality. For each goBTC issued a carbon credit is also issued to neutralise its previous carbon footprint. To learn more visit https://algomint.io or to start bridging BTC to Algorand visit https://app.algomint.io
